segments.text: Ladies and gentlemen, AM 980, WRC, the talk station, presents the Mike Cuthbert Show with your host, Mike Cuthbert.
News with John Megley, WRC all-day traffic, weather from the Weather Channel, and your participation at 202-882-WRC1.
Free mobile calls at Star WRC on Bell Atlantic and pound 980 on Cellular One.
1109 here at WRC, and our phones are open.
They soon probably will be filled, so call early for the book guy, Alan Stipek, who's here.

He makes his, well, I suppose every two months we try to have Alan on because, first of all, he gives lots of you a lot of good value, and second of all, as all my friends say and some of my enemies when they meet me, you know that guy, every time he's on, I think, ah, books.
But I always learn something I never knew before about either books or literature or history or something.

bookstore of its kind on the East Coast.
